data.description: This home is extended and expanded, one of a kind!  Enter into a foyer w/ laun. room &  storage.  Garage entrance ,over sized w/workshop.  Large eat-in kitchen w/island & wood burnung insert. Both baths are updated. Extended bedroom on 1st floor. Den w/ FPL and Living room with sliders to patio. Bedrooms upstairs are dormered with huge master w/walk-in closet.  New ceramic flooring in Den, LR & DR.  All Andersen windows.  Paved driveway and patio. Fully fenced oversized yard. CAC. Gas boiler is 12 years, brand new expansion tank, HW heater is 7 years. Roof on rt & garage is 2yrs, rest is 12
